{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840026334,"sessionID":"ses_287b0274affey6JR54kD5vrgQq","part":{"id":"prt_d78505e6c001o5MCb2xPy4xBwZ","messageID":"msg_d785030a1001taibRooSjr2mw8","sessionID":"ses_287b0274affey6JR54kD5vrgQq","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-37fff8c3a30b44fbb038fb8851b4fd9d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/test_spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/test_spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube 测试用例规范 (TDD Specification)\n2: \n3: 要求 AI 在实现业务代码时，同步完成以下测试用例，作为实现完成度的判定标准。\n4: \n5: ## 1. 核心控制器测试 (Workload Manager)\n6: - **TestCase-WM-001**: 验证 Sandbox 创建接口。输入合法 `AgentRuntime` 定义，预期返回 `200 OK` 及 `sessionId`。\n7: - **TestCase-WM-002**: 验证 Sandbox 幂等性。相同 `name` 连续调用两次，预期返回相同 `sessionId`。\n8: - **TestCase-WM-003**: 验证非法输入拦截。输入缺失 `podTemplate` 的请求，预期返回 `400 Bad Request`。\n9: \n10: ## 2. 路由与会话测试 (Router)\n11: - **TestCase-RT-001**: 验证 Auth 拦截。未携带 Bearer Token 请求 `/v1/execute`，预期返回 `401 Unauthorized`。\n12: - **TestCase-RT-002**: 验证会话路由。模拟 Redis 中存在会话，Router 成功将请求转发至后端（Mock 后端）。\n13: - **TestCase-RT-003**: 验证会话过期。模拟 Redis 中 Token 已失效，返回 `404 Not Found`。\n14: \n15: ## 3. 存储层测试 (Store)\n16: - **TestCase-ST-001**: Redis Set/Get 验证。成功存储并检索 `SessionInfo` 结构体。\n17: - **TestCase-ST-002**: 过期时间验证。验证 Key 携带正确的 TTL（默认 24h）。\n18: \n19: ## 4. 编码执行引擎测试 (PicoD)\n20: - **TestCase-PD-001**: Python 代码执行。发送 `print(\"hello\")`，预期 stdout 为 `hello\\n`，exitCode 为 0。\n21: - **TestCase-PD-002**: 错误处理。发送语法错误代码，预期 stderr 包含 `SyntaxError`。\n22: \n23: ## 5. Python SDK 测试\n24: - **TestCase-SDK-001**: 上下文管理器验证。使用 `with CodeInterpreterClient(...) as client:` 确保结束时自动调用 `close()`。\n25: - **TestCase-SDK-002**: 异常映射。服务端返回 500 时，SDK 抛出自定义 `AgentCubeError` 而非原始 HTTP 错误。\n26: \n27: ## 实施要求\n28: - **Go 代码**：必须位于对应的 `*_test.go` 中，可通过 `go test ./...` 运行。\n29: - **Python 代码**：必须位于 `tests/` 目录或 `test_*.py` 文件中，可通过 `pytest` 运行。\n\n(End of file - total 29 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube 测试用例规范 (TDD Specification)\n\n要求 AI 在实现业务代码时，同步完成以下测试用例，作为实现完成度的判定标准。\n\n## 1. 核心控制器测试 (Workload Manager)\n- **TestCase-WM-001**: 验证 Sandbox 创建接口。输入合法 `AgentRuntime` 定义，预期返回 `200 OK` 及 `sessionId`。\n- **TestCase-WM-002**: 验证 Sandbox 幂等性。相同 `name` 连续调用两次，预期返回相同 `sessionId`。\n- **TestCase-WM-003**: 验证非法输入拦截。输入缺失 `podTemplate` 的请求，预期返回 `400 Bad Request`。\n\n## 2. 路由与会话测试 (Router)\n- **TestCase-RT-001**: 验证 Auth 拦截。未携带 Bearer Token 请求 `/v1/execute`，预期返回 `401 Unauthorized`。\n- **TestCase-RT-002**: 验证会话路由。模拟 Redis 中存在会话，Router 成功将请求转发至后端（Mock 后端）。\n- **TestCase-RT-003**: 验证会话过期。模拟 Redis 中 Token 已失效，返回 `404 Not Found`。\n\n## 3. 存储层测试 (Store)\n- **TestCase-ST-001**: Redis Set/Get 验证。成功存储并检索 `SessionInfo` 结构体。\n- **TestCase-ST-002**: 过期时间验证。验证 Key 携带正确的 TTL（默认 24h）。\n\n## 4. 编码执行引擎测试 (PicoD)\n- **TestCase-PD-001**: Python 代码执行。发送 `print(\"hello\")`，预期 stdout 为 `hello\\n`，exitCode 为 0。","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/test_spec.md","time":{"start":1775840026324,"end":1775840026333}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840026338,"sessionID":"ses_287b0274affey6JR54kD5vrgQq","part":{"id":"prt_d78505b0c001EWn8JAXUitwXGE","messageID":"msg_d785030a1001taibRooSjr2mw8","sessionID":"ses_287b0274affey6JR54kD5vrgQq","type":"tool","tool":"glob","callID":"toolu_tool-955cf990b3a8435791b57c00dad45914","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"path":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z","pattern":"**/*spec*.md"},"output":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/spec.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/deployment/delta-spec.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/test_spec.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/integrations/spec.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/sandbox-orchestration/spec.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/ci-cd/spec.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/idle-cleanup/spec.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/python-sdk/spec.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/session-store/spec.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/deployment/spec.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/session-routing/spec.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/cli-toolkit/spec.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/code-execution/spec.md","metadata":{"count":14,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z","time":{"start":1775840026320,"end":1775840026336}}}}
