 Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义 AgentRuntime CRD 的 Go 类型结构，包括:\n- `AgentRuntime` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n- `AgentRuntimeList` 类型\n- `CodeInterpreter` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n- `CodeInterpreterList` 类型\n- 相关常量、标签、注解定义","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md","time":{"start":1775840031945,"end":1775840031961}}}}
