{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840115335,"sessionID":"ses_287b0274affey6JR54kD5vrgQq","part":{"id":"prt_d7851ba62001rBJIj1AMw0o7LD","messageID":"msg_d7850751e001njuEjESxi2eaCw","sessionID":"ses_287b0274affey6JR54kD5vrgQq","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-89317ca0b18a4aeb90ce6d3e24d759ad","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Delta Spec: AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter Type Definition\n\n**Module:** `pkg/apis`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S\n\n---\n\n## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n\n### Requirement: Package structure and registration\n\nThe system SHALL define the `CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` with proper package structure, scheme registration, and CRD markers for controller-gen.\n\n#### Scenario: Package structure exists\n- **GIVEN** the repository root at `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n- **WHEN** examining `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n- **THEN** the directory SHALL contain:\n  - `doc.go` with `+k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` marker\n  - `register.go` with `SchemeGroupVersion` set to `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n  - `codeinterpreter_types.go` with `CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` types\n  - `shared_types.go` with `AuthModeType` enum and `TargetPort` type\n  - `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` (generated)\n\n#### Scenario: Scheme group version is correct\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the file\n- **THEN** `GroupVersion` SHALL be `schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}`\n\n#### Scenario: CodeInterpreter Kind registration\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the file\n- **THEN** `CodeInterpreterKind` SHALL be `\"CodeInterpreter\"`\n- AND `CodeInterpreterListKind` SHALL be `\"CodeInterpreterList\"`\n- AND `CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind` SHALL be `GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: CodeInterpreter type definition\n\nThe system SHALL define `CodeInterpreter` as a Kubernetes-style typed object with `TypeMeta`, `ObjectMeta`, `Spec`, and `Status`.\n\n#### Scenario: CodeInterpreter struct shape\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the `CodeInterpreter` struct definition\n- **THEN** the struct SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta` and have `Spec CodeInterpreterSpec` and `Status CodeInterpreterStatus` fields with JSON tags `spec` and `status`\n\n#### Scenario: CodeInterpreterList struct shape\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the `CodeInterpreterList` struct definition\n- **THEN** the struct SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta`, have `metav1.ListMeta` with JSON tag `metadata`, and `Items []CodeInterpreter` with JSON tag `items`\n\n#### Scenario: CRD markers on CodeInterpreter\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n- **WHEN** examining type-level markers\n- **THEN** the `CodeInterpreter` type SHALL have:\n  - `+genclient` marker\n  - `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object` marker\n  - `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` marker\n  - `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` marker\n  - `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced` marker\n  - `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"` marker\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: CodeInterpreterSpec definition\n\nThe system SHALL define `CodeInterpreterSpec` with fields for sandbox template, session management, warm pool, and authentication.\n\n#### Scenario: CodeInterpreterSpec fields\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct\n- **THEN** the struct SHALL contain fields:\n  - `Ports []TargetPort` with JSON tag `ports` (optional)\n  - `Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` with JSON tag `template` (required)\n  - `SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration` with JSON tag `sessionTimeout` (optional, default 15m)\n  - `MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration` with JSON tag `maxSessionDuration` (optional, default 8h)\n  - `WarmPoolSize *int32` with JSON tag `warmPoolSize` (optional)\n  - `AuthMode AuthModeType` with JSON tag `authMode` (optional, default picod)\n\n#### Scenario: Template field is required\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n- **WHEN** examining the `Template` field markers\n- **THEN** it SHALL have `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` marker\n\n#### Scenario: SessionTimeout default\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n- **WHEN** examining the `SessionTimeout` field marker\n- **THEN** it SHALL have `+kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"` marker\n\n#### Scenario: MaxSessionDuration default\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n- **WHEN** examining the `MaxSessionDuration` field marker\n- **THEN** it SHALL have `+kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"` marker\n\n#### Scenario: AuthMode enum and default\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n- **WHEN** examining the `AuthMode` field marker\n- **THEN** it SHALL have:\n  - `+kubebuilder:default=picod` marker\n  - `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none` marker\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate definition\n\nThe system SHALL define `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` for configuring code interpreter pods.\n\n#### Scenario: CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate fields\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` struct\n- **THEN** the struct SHALL contain:\n  - `Labels map[string]string` with JSON tag `labels` (optional)\n  - `Annotations map[string]string` with JSON tag `annotations` (optional)\n  - `RuntimeClassName *string` with JSON tag `runtimeClassName` (optional)\n  - `Image string` with JSON tag `image` (optional)\n  - `ImagePullPolicy corev1.PullPolicy` with JSON tag `imagePullPolicy` (optional)\n  - `ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference` with JSON tag `imagePullSecrets` (optional)\n  - `Environment []corev1.EnvVar` with JSON tag `environment` (optional)\n  - `Command []string` with JSON tag `command` (optional)\n  - `Args []string` with JSON tag `args` (optional)\n  - `Resources corev1.ResourceRequirements` with JSON tag `resources` (optional)\n\n#### Scenario: ImagePullSecrets list markers\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n- **WHEN** examining the `ImagePullSecrets` field\n- **THEN** it SHALL have:\n  - `+patchMergeKey=name` marker\n  - `+patchStrategy=merge` marker\n  - `+listType=map` marker\n  - `+listMapKey=name` marker\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: CodeInterpreterStatus definition\n\nThe system SHALL define `CodeInterpreterStatus` with conditions and readiness flag.\n\n#### Scenario: CodeInterpreterStatus fields\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the `CodeInterpreterStatus` struct\n- **THEN** the struct SHALL contain:\n  - `Conditions []metav1.Condition` with JSON tag `conditions` (optional)\n  - `Ready bool` with JSON tag `ready` (optional)\n\n#### Scenario: Conditions field markers\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n- **WHEN** examining the `Conditions` field\n- **THEN** it SHALL have:\n  - `+optional` marker\n  - `+listType=atomic` marker\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: AuthModeType enum definition\n\nThe system SHALL define `AuthModeType` in `shared_types.go` as an enum for authentication modes.\n\n#### Scenario: AuthModeType type definition\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the file\n- **THEN** `AuthModeType` SHALL be defined as `type AuthModeType string`\n\n#### Scenario: AuthModeType constants\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the file\n- **THEN** the following constants SHALL be defined:\n  - `AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod